5:
Wowie! Look at that line! What's
going on?
8:
Well... It seems word has gotten
around about your powers...
12:
Everyone here wants to ask you for a
dream.
17:
Whoa... So all these people have
someone they really, REALLY wanna
meet, huh?
21:
A lot of folks in Palpebra are working
away from home, and... Many have
also lost someone precious to them
in the Kaleidoscope...
25:
You could say Palpebra has a
surplus of lonely individuals.
30:
I'll prepare an extra large reward, so
please, Feanie, take the job! Just this
once!
36:
O-okay! I'll do my best, just like any
good girl should!
42:
Hehe... It's kinda like we're all having
a sleepover.
45:
Well, doing this one at a time would
take forever... Will you be okay
managing everyone at once?
54:
All right, then Lilie and I shall be
waiting outside. Let us know if you
need—
59:
Nooo, Light, you should stay here! I
wanna take a nap with you!
69: ...Fine. I shall stay here with you.
77:
Okay, everybody! Lay down, close
your eyes, and think of the person
you want to see again. Time to go to
bed!
81:
Warm and fluffy, soft and fuzzy... 
A touching reunion ahead...
91:
*sniff* I never thought I'd see them
again! Waaah!
94:
Good, good... Looks like everybody
got to see their loved ones...
102:
Hehe... I'm fine. I just went a teensy
bit overboard.
105:
Perhaps we should not do such
large groups in the future...
109:
Aww... But having naptime with this
many people was kinda nice...
112:
When I see them smiling after
reuniting with someone they miss, 
I can't help but smile too.
121:
Mmm, yummy! Now I've got plenty
of energy.
125:
Thanks again for today, Feanie! All
the participants today were super
grateful.
129: Hehe, yaaay! I was the goodest girl!
132:
What about you, Light? Did you see
the person you wanted to?
139:
No... I didn't have a dream of any
kind.
144:
Huh? Really? Oh... I guess I didn't do
as good a job as I thought...
147: No, I don't think it was your doing.
150:
I simply have no one I wish to see in
my dreams.
153:
...Although there are plenty I wish I
could have saved...
156: I see... So that's what you want...
162:
I think... I might be the same way...
but different...
165:
I wanna see my mama... But I wanna
see her in real life, not a dream...
167:
Maybe that's why I've never
dreamed about her before...
170: Yes... I think that might be it.
174:
You know... The people you helped
today really are grateful. They know
about your situation, so I'm sure if
any of them happen upon your
parents, they'll let us know.
177:
The Guild now knows to keep an eye
out too. If your parents show up
here, you'll be reunited in no time.
188:
You helped a lot of people here. It's
only fair that they return the favor.
196:
Never seeing her in my dreams
made thinking about my mama
sad, but now... I'm excited for the day
I get to meet her!
199:
In fact, I think I have even more
energy than before!
203:
I'm gonna help out lots and lots to
show my parents what a good girl I
am!
